        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="4"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="5"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="6"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="item active">
                    <img class="d-block img" src="~/Content/images/slide1.jpg" alt="First slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h3>Alte Götter erwarten neue Götter!</h3>
                        <p>Der ewige Kampf um das perfekte Deck ist eröffnet</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="d-block img" src="~/Content/images/slide2.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h3>Karten, Karten, Karten!</h3>
                        <p>Alles dreht sich um DIE richtige Karte</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="d-block img" src="~/Content/images/slide3.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h3>Ewige Wildniss</h3>
                        <p>Ewiger Frieden - nicht bei uns - Kämpft bis das letzte Deck vernichtet wurde.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="d-block img" src="~/Content/images/slide4.jpg" alt="First slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h3>Heute schon ...</h3>
                        <p>Ragnaros besieht? Oder doch nur einen Murloc? Schau hinein und finde es heraus</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="d-block img" src="~/Content/images/slide5.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h3>Gnome an dich Macht!</h3>
                        <p>Klein aber OHO! Nicht nur ein Motto für Gnome.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="d-block img" src="~/Content/images/slide6.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h3>Orcs vs. Humans</h3>
                        <p>Schon seit Anbeginn der Zeit der Kampf um die Vorherrschaft</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="d-block img" src="~/Content/images/slide7.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h3>Ghul'Kehzdan will dich!</h3>
                        <p>und belegt dich mit dem ewigen Kartenfluch!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

